    "name": "AgentIF",
    "description": "\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\t[NeurlPS 2025] AgentIF: Benchmarking Instruction Following of Large Language Models in Agentic Scenarios\n\t\n\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tOverview\n\t\n\nAgentIF is the first benchmark designed to systematically evaluate the instruction-following capabilities of large language models (LLMs) in agentic scenarios. It consists of instructions and constraints derived from real-world agent-based applications, enabling fine-grained, executable evaluation.\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\t\tKey Features\n\t\n\n\nRealistic\nBuilt from 50 real-world… See the full description on the dataset page: https://huggingface.co/datasets/THU-KEG/AgentIF.",
